# Module: Machine Learning - Classification

## Outline
This course will cover:
* Introduction to binary classification with scikit-learn
* The main classification metrics (confusion matrix, precision, recall, ...)
* The K-nearest neighbors algorithm
* Grid search on classifiers

## Excercises & Tasks

There is one notebook to be completed, where the missing code is denoted by the comment *#TOFILL*, along with a memo that contains questions about the notebook exercises. Both come with their corrected versions with answers.
